{{zh-forms|[[早知今日，何必当初]]|[[早]][[知]][[今日]]，[[何必當初]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: zăo zhī jīnrì, hébìdāngchū
===Etymology===
Literally: If I would have known about this day from the beginning, there would have been no point in starting.
===Idiom===
# to regret something you did in the past

===Synonyms===
*[[既有今日，何必當初]], [[既有今日，何必当初]]

